WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.700
Just fighting trash?

00:00:01.700 --> 00:00:03.500
Yeah, so what?

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:06.200
Because I know how to put this thing to work,

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:08.620
that's all that matters.

00:00:08.620 --> 00:00:12.200
Weight, smell, texture, I know it better than anyone.

00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:14.120
And while you're playing around in the mud,

00:00:14.120 --> 00:00:16.679
I wake up day after day to ask how it's doing.

00:00:16.679 --> 00:00:19.120
And day after day after every damn day,

00:00:19.120 --> 00:00:21.120
I bash everything with a big old swing

00:00:21.120 --> 00:00:25.039
to see where, how fast, and how far it flies.

00:00:25.039 --> 00:00:26.640
Am I making any sense to you?

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:28.440
Or do I need to show you what I mean?

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:33.000
Fine, but don't say I didn't warn you!

00:00:48.719 --> 00:00:49.219
Sucker.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:09.299
Come on, is that all?

00:01:09.299 --> 00:01:10.640
Just one hit did the trick.

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:12.000
You'll be just as easy.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:01.840
So make sure you give it a shot today you little coward.

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:03.920
I'm sorry but I don't know what to say to you now Sucker.

00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:06.959
I still hope you do a good job right now.

00:02:06.959 --> 00:02:08.500
I'll get some coffee today,

00:02:08.500 --> 00:02:10.460
and let you rice it up one day.

00:02:10.460 --> 00:02:11.800
I really appreciate that.

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:13.300
You said it.

00:02:13.300 --> 00:02:14.139
Forget it.

00:02:14.139 --> 00:02:15.740
Or I'll win.

00:02:15.740 --> 00:02:17.099
I ball you guys are such�

00:02:20.139 --> 00:02:21.759
It's so sweet.

00:02:24.659 --> 00:02:26.080
Are you sure I can practice earlier?

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:26.719
Yeah.

00:02:26.719 --> 00:02:28.680
How are you feeling?

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:29.879
What's the involves?

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:59.979
Thank you for watching!

